Kerfen ifassen-is. 
Kerfen iḍaṛen-is.
Cetwa neɣ tagrest kifkif, d taqbaylit akk.
Ferḥat yumen s tmurt taqbaylit.
Umneɣ yiwen wass taqbaylit ad d-yeflali fell-as yiṭij.
Tafat d lwiz i uderɣal.
Ǧǧiɣ tamurt acḥal aya.
Tergagi tasa-w mi sliɣ s tmettant-is.
Teǧǧel meskint d tameẓyant.
Ah...! A lammer sɛiɣ taxatemt n sidi Sliman!
Cfiɣ, d awezɣi ad ttuɣ.
Aqbayli yettwet ɣer tkatut, teḍṛa-as am win ihelken alzaymer.
Asif aɛisi yuɣal d Wad aɛisi, ma d At yanni uɣalen d Benni yenni. 
Nniɣ-d ala lmeɛna-s ala! 
Swiɣ yiwet n tberkant, ukiɣ-d din din. 
Swiɣ yiwet n tebyirt yekkes-iyi fad. 
Ur lliɣ d amasiḥi, d aɛrab neɣ d ineslem, nek d aqbayli. 
Tqerḥeḍ iman-ik baṭṭel. 
D akud i d ddwa n leǧruḥ. 
D asirem i ddwa n facal. 
Kullec ad iɛeddi, imeṭṭawen-im ad kawen.
Kullec ad iɛeddi, imeṭṭawen-ik ad kawen. 
Izri d ayen iɛeddan, imal d ayen id-teddun, tudert d imir-a. 
Swiɣ afenǧal n lgazuz asemmaḍ. 
Ččiɣ tacakulat yesɛan sebɛin ɣef meyya n kakao. 
Wissen ma d tidet tella tudert umbaɛd lmut?
Wissen amek ad as-nḥulfu i lmut ass tmijalt-nneɣ. 
Nek ma ḥemleɣ yiwen qqareɣ-as-t. 




